                        <p></p>
<p itemprop="description">
A Jewish man has a wonderful romance with the help of his humour, but must use that same quality to protect his son in a Nazi death camp.</p>
                        <p></p>
    <div class="txt-block" itemprop="director" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
